### Crear item
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/inventory
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "profileId": "{{profileId}}",
  "quantity": 150.00,
  "location": "Estante A1",
  "costPriceEur": 450.00,
  "supplier": "Aceros S.A.",
  "notes": "Lote de vigas HEB200"
}

### Listar items
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/inventory?page=0&size=20
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### Obtener item por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/inventory/{{itemId}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### Actualizar item
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/inventory/{{itemId}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 200.00,
  "location": "Estante B2",
  "costPriceEur": 420.00,
  "supplier": "Aceros del Sur",
  "notes": "Reabastecido"
}

### Eliminar item
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/inventory/{{itemId}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
